Author: red_ossifrage
Text: I know, I'm sorry. Not eating is basically the only thing that makes me emotionally capable of dealing with my mom's drama, and my relatives' enabling of that drama.  I just wish I could have a normal life for one day. Unfortunately, my ED is the only thing that makes things feel normal (which I recognize is insane).   I'm so sorry you're struggling too.
